item.description:
Sorry about the last minute notice, but I hope you can all join us!!!

If you've ever wanted to be a star, now is your time to shine!! Please join us for a fun evening of singing. You don't HAVE to participate, it's just as much fun be in the audience.

We will be meeting at 8 pm to get something to eat before the singing begins. Karaoke starts at 9 pm and runs until 1am.

Hope to see you all there!!

Ivone

http://www.lavenderas...
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the Ivone or the Fun Single party
item.name: Let's sing - Karaoke style!!!
